HEADWORD: Bee line
<hw>Bee" line`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>The shortest line from one
place to another, like that of a bee to its hive when loaded with honey;
an air line.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>bee line</xex> for the brig.⟦rdquo⟧
